[[File:The Lord of the Rings Trading Card Game - Halbarad, Ranger of the North.jpg|thumb|Halbarad in ''[[The Lord of the Rings Trading Card Game]]'']]'''Warren Mahy''' ([[29 September|September 29]], [[1969]]) is a designer, illustrator and sculptor from [[New Zealand]]. He has worked with [[Weta Workshop]] for [[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|''The Lord of the Rings'' (film series)]], contributed to the ''[[Isengard (LOTRRPG)|Isengard]]'' supplement by [[Decipher]] and appeared as [[Halbarad]] on a [[Decipher Card]].
